          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Ensuring the Safety of Our Mail Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to increase from 5 to 10 years the maximum prison term for a defendant who commits mail theft. <b><br /></b></p>]]></text>
